release_note: What s new in Movavi 4.3.1: Introducing our enhanced video editor for a smooth editing experience. It couldn t be more user friendly enjoy! Say goodbye to boring backgrounds our AI powered photo module will instantly enhance your photos Start making art on the fly with our new collage feature Meet our fresh new main screen! Important: Be aware that you won t be able to access any unsaved projects when updating from earlier versions. We also want you to know that some features in the video editor are currently unavailable but we ll add them in future updates. Stay tuned for our next updates and check back soon!

Even more stable than before!

Making smooth transitions has never been easier with the audio fade in out function. Don t be concerned about accidentally deleting all the stickers text and music that you ve added. The new autosave feature will make your experience even more carefree. Now more stable than ever!

To make your photos look exciting and lively the pan and zoom effect is applied to all photos automatically. Minor stability improvements.

Your favorite photos will no longer get left out. Now you can add them to your movie! String several photos together to make a cool slideshow. Adjust photo duration to any length from 0.1 to 10 seconds. The new home screen helps you start making videos and slideshows right away.

Christmas is coming! Try our free Christmas themed stickers give your videos that special holiday touch. You can never have too many stickers.
